<h1 id="toc0"><span>SCP基金会安保设施档案</span></h1>
<h3 id="toc1"><span>Lunar Area-32</span></h3>
<p><strong>官方名称：</strong> SCP基金会月球专业化研究与收容站点</p>
<p><strong>站点识别码：</strong> LMaImb-Area-32</p>
</div>
<hr />
<div style="text-align: center;">
<h2 id="toc2"><span>基本信息</span></h2>
</div>
<hr />
<div class="scp-image-block block-right" style="width:300px;"><a href="/local--files/secure-facility-dossier-lunar-area-32/Imbrium.png" target="_blank"><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/secure-facility-dossier-lunar-area-32/Imbrium.png" style="width:300px;" alt="Imbrium.png" class="image" /></a>
